Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zabi family seeks to impose\Na dictatorship over all of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...ruling from the Principality of Zeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...a giant space city-state\Nfloating beyond the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader of the Zabi family,\NGihren Zabi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...waged war against the Earth Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...in order to make all of humanity\Nkneel before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After evading a Zeon attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base escaped from\Nthe space city Side 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...and landed on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there was to be no brief rest\Nfor the young crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For Amuro, burdened by his parting\Nfrom his mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...it seemed that his troubles only increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Time, Be Still
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's wishing victory\Nto the Principality of Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, this is boring!\N- Get off the stage...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How long is this going to go on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather have one more bullet\Nthan you bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Giyal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No point in getting mad at the pigeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck in this border zone, polishing Zakus!\NOf course I'm angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that, come on down.\NI have something to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?\NIsn't the recreation corps visiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's boring with just a bunch of guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, the Federation's mobile suits\Nare in action around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sol's a comm officer reporting directly\Nto the commander and I heard it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Is our squad heading out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. They wouldn't send us.\NWe're just a patrol squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And given how cautious our boss is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not going to start anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're thinking of taking on those mobile suits\Njust with us younger guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How many do we have to deal with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we're doing it on our own...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...the boss says we can try\Nbeating them if we like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If it goes well, they'll send us home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to nice, clean, bug-free Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's only my one Zaku in this squad.\NWhat are you guys going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him the plan, Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They only have one mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was made in a rush, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The engine maintenance will be\Ncompleted by dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not part of the regular forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why are you re-supplying us\Nand making repairs for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation will not\Nabandon the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they do intend to send you\Na superior officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a big offensive\Nbeing planned in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, the Federation\Ndoesn't have the luxury of sending...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...relief personnel to a unit like yours\Nwhich is holding its own in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeon is in the same situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the White Base's main mission\Nis data collection at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Data collection?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Amateurs tend to devise more\Ninteresting tactics than pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We collect those tactics\Nfrom the computers' memory banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you ignore us on purpose\Nto use as guinea pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like being a guinea pig,\NEnsign Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't received any such orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's what General Revil said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be notified soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure like to jerk us around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for General Revil,\Nyou would've been executed long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Executed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be asleep right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Mr. Bright says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep is part of a pilot's job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it such a crime to have taken control\Nof the White Base and Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ensign Bright Noa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The toilet's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?\N- Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me, Haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, have you had your meal already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Have you had your meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to breach\Nthe Zeon patrol network, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the Gundam ready on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright. This is the escape route\Nof Matilda's craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the White Base.\NBoth routes are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Will they let us escape?\N- That depends on the Zeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a flash of light ahead to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Minovsky particles are dense.\NWe can't identify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send out a signal flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That patrol isn't listed on the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No response to the flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us lower.\NWe'll escape at combat speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare anti-aircraft guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a Medea transport.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's flying at maximum combat speed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it's not carrying any cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have unloaded the cargo\Nsomewhere near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Could it be related to the Trojan Horse\Nthat Chief Cuaran was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible. Send out a flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Help get the Zaku ready!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tell the boss we're moving out.\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I launch an attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...the enemy will send out\Ntheir mobile suit too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? Be sure to tell Cuaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Petty Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuaran, don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Chief Cuaran!\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sol, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When the mobile suit comes out,\Nwe follow the plan we discussed last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that we get to go home\Nif this is a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sol! Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a racket, so early in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That Cuaran guy is always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is. The Medea transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Return fire at 1 o'clock.\NAnd get lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That style of attack can only be a Zaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Skim over the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty bold for a big target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If those Lugguns were covering me, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A direct hit to the container!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter! Just keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser reading... The Medea's in combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Medea's been snared by a Zeon patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base will provide support.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Bright! I'll go In the Gundam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The White Base's supply work\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's right, but...\NYou want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir! I'll launch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope nothing's happened to Ms. Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation's mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- He didn't have to come.\N- Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's accept the Gundam's kindness\Nand escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay safe, Ms. Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pursue it too far, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those soldiers are unprotected!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Facing the Gundam with machine guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of attack are they planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! Why am I shaking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide under the trees!\NYou'll get hit from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those? What are they planning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the weak spots on the armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Answer me! Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you destroy the Zaku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Can you answer me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy ship is here! Retreat and aim\Nat the bombs on the mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lousy pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is hit one of\Nthe bombs we attached, and it's toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!\NDon't you dare take me for a fool! I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My shield...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exploded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it!\NThey were planting bombs on the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're going to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This must be one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How many did they plant on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, what's wrong?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They've planted bombs all over the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a good spot, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll move to the meadow up ahead and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Omur!\NHe knows all about bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we have to wait 30 minutes\Nfor our bomb timers to go off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be that way. I never thought\Nwe'd be able to plant them so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think those guys\Ncan save the mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If it turns out like this,\NI really wish we had remote control bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be KABOOM by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a patrol squad like us\Nnever gets the good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But can they remove\Nthe bombs in 30 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's five left, right?\NAfter the one that blew up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be quite the spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:16:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can definitely say that\Nthe timer on this bomb is functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, can you tell anything\Nfrom the x-ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all I can tell is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This thin wire should work like a time fuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if we try to tear off\Nthe plastic explosive from the magnet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...it'll explode, right, Mr. Omur?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice but to take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But this is my responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand back, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be no time left at all.\NI'll get started on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the pilot's removing the bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If they have any common sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...they should know the bombs will explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're removing them anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...12 minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's removed the second bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, for a Federation pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he on the third?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they've got the crane up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,8 minutes left. Will he make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't we all helping him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we all help, it'll be done quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They might explode any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to minimize the casualties...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...Amuro's the only one who can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mirai, you're a hypocrite too!\NYou're a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Restraining yourself is also brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let you sacrifice yourself\Nalong with Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be the other way around!\NAmuro's a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, could you do\Na better job than Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mirai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're cruel...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If these explode now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that's It for Gundam, and for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's one or two left, right?\N- Should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have noticed the timers by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's keeping at it despite that,\Nhe's got to be pretty brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty brave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's not coming out.\N- Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's around the back, right?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. If it's just raising a leg or arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, stay on the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,1 minute, 20 seconds.\NCan they do it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Hurry! It's taken too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We're going 1 kilometer out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. They removed them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Another 18 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we won't be going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're not the only ones\Nrisking our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I wonder what the fool\Nwho removed the bombs is like!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- More, please.\N- Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? There's a car coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a civilian truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a station wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. In a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is this a Zeon mobile suit?\N- I don't think so... Looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people? Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just some young guys\Nfrom around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Federation mobile suit, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the guy in the white there\Nperhaps the mobile suit pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hurt yourself, Mr. Pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look so angry, Mr. Pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good fight, soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,People who live on Earth are so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:22:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were the ones who planted the bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan is a brave Zeon veteran who has been molded by the dreadful war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro hates having to fight a man who only wants to protect war orphans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan's emotions leave a strong impression on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Cucuruz Doan's Island."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cucuruz Doan's Island
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:59.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:10.13,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:15.05,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:25.06,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:29.65,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:39.95,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:59.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:10.13,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:15.05,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:25.06,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:29.65,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:39.95,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
